{"tid":2189320,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"理想既十二年免費教育","createTime":"2020-09-04T20:34:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T05:17:45.000Z","uid":364074,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"90088a5f7139029364010231d8151a6be09a20e8","tid":2189320,"uid":364074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T20:34:33.000Z","msg":"大家覺得理想既十二年免費教育 應該有D咩?<br />\n<br />\n學校有D咩係教左, 但不合時宜? 教左, 但教既方法poorly taught而且你大個左睇翻轉頭先知係咩? 有D咩係好重要, 但無教? <br />\n<br />\n教育, 應該納入D咩 係啟發倒人個種?  我抛磚引玉:<br />\n<br />\n例如文科, 可介紹藝術家手稿,  哲學, 社會學 思想流派, 欣賞有影響力既電影, <br />\n<br />\n科學嘗試重溫以前既實驗, 分析科學理論既係現實可以實踐既方面及可能性, <br />\n<br />\n數學, 適應抽象思考, 與符號邏輯學一同學習<br />\n<br />\n電腦, 學習基本programming, 將科技融入校園<br />\n<br />\n鼓勵辯論, 不停思考個種可能性, 學會深入思考<br />\n<br />\n心理學, 人際關係學, 幫學生認識自己, 了解自己既氣質同性格, 注意自己溝通既弱點, 了解自己同咩人夾, 加強心理健康既認知, 學會與自己情緒溝通. <br />\n <br />\n我lum倒既係咁多"},{"pid":"6d35b3ef1315c8beffb4b8e6971fc40aad90ede9","tid":2189320,"uid":312363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T20:39:31.000Z","msg":"烏托邦教育<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2ca1254eafb42ab05b6d5f7de185983ff76054b","tid":2189320,"uid":364074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d35b3ef1315c8beffb4b8e6971fc40aad90ede9","tid":2189320,"uid":312363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T20:39:31.000Z","msg":"烏托邦教育<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T20:41:57.000Z","msg":"姐係點, 教柏拉圖?? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eacec703c9c8e761ac4618f3bf1f55fb382c977","tid":2189320,"uid":364074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d35b3ef1315c8beffb4b8e6971fc40aad90ede9","tid":2189320,"uid":312363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T20:39:31.000Z","msg":"烏托邦教育<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T20:42:47.000Z","msg":"一切都源於